Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.72,0:00:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That Sunday... I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.74,0:00:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What made you want to come to\Nthe park all of a sudden, Emi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.99,0:00:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on down, it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be a pianist!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:00:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At the top of the jungle gym,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.30,0:01:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I chose a future as a pianist.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.39,0:01:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I abandoned all my other infinite\Npossibilities, and chose that one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.10,0:01:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come back! Come back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.27,0:01:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.73,0:01:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, where are your manners?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.15,0:01:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do?\NI'm Yuriko Ochiai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.57,0:01:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.16,0:01:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.37,0:01:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.04,0:01:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that people who hear me will think,\N"I want to be a pianist, too..."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.38,0:01:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will I be able to play\Nthe piano like that, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.05,0:01:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish for it hard enough, Emi-chan,\NI'm sure that the music will respond to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.81,0:01:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The piano will listen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:01:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can I play it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:01:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only kind\Nof sound I can make...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the sounds that boy made{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.67,0:02:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}were just like sunflowers...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.80,0:02:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kousei Arima, who I yearned to be like.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.55,0:02:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Every great performer played \Nfor the first time at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.97,0:02:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even Mozart, even Beethoven.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.14,0:02:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even the person who made you\Nthink, "I want to become a pianist."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What will you pour into your piano playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.65,0:02:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What wish will you ask it to grant you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.66,0:02:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to play the piano like that boy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:03:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to stand on the same stage as him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That way, I just know...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.47,0:03:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That I'll be able to see what he sees.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let it ring... Let it ring... My piano!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let it ring.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.51,0:05:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that girl for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:16.30,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Entrance to Greenrooms
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good job. You were amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? What?\NYou confessing your love?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.27,0:06:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go change.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.48,0:06:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Before you catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just spill it already!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:07:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now...there's no need for words.\NBecause I poured all my feelings into the piano.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.41,0:07:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There will now be an intermission.\NJudging will resume in fifteen minutes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that girl who just left?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.01,0:07:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a pile of medication.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, just spotted a hot girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Tsubaki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.48,0:07:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The closer it gets to Kousei's turn, my stomach...\NIt's so much easier to deal with my own matches!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you're the one\Nwho'll be playing, Tsubaki-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.28,0:07:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so just sit back and relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but is Kousei gonna be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just spotted an angelic older woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He could be quaking in his shoes\Nafter that amazing performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that's so not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cause you know what, he's a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We will now resume judging.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thump, thump. My heart's\Npounding even harder than before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.62,0:08:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arima's choice of piece today\Nis Chopin's Etude Op. 25 No. 5{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Inconceivable!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Till now, Arima's always showcased his ability\Nto play difficult pieces without a false note.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.51,0:08:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why I challenged him\Nwith my Op. 25, No. 11...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.68,0:08:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure Takeshi did, too...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the song Arima chose to play today\Ncan't be considered a difficult piece...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.06,0:08:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's inconceivable.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:08:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did you pick out Kousei's piece?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.03,0:09:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It landed on 25-5, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You used a pencil to decide?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.91,0:09:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A pencil...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't matter what piece he played.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.42,0:09:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As long as he entered the competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It really didn't matter at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.97,0:09:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei Arima.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.01,0:09:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.22,0:09:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just by placing himself in this particular\Nspace, he's sure to feel stimulated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.31,0:09:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he won't feel provoked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.86,0:09:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The other pianists won't let him\Nhang back. They won't allow him to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Arima-kun's a musician.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is so strange. Is it\Nbecause it's been two years?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My heart is pounding.\NIt's so hot, and so violent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.54,0:10:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it because I watched those two perform?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without holding back, grasping with both\Nhands, shaking my soul to its very core.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Check it out - this is who I am.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Watch me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.52,0:10:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm the same as you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.27,0:10:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the clock's hands will move.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Time will start flowing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kao-chan...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.86,0:10:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I never knew. That music could be this\Ncolorful, and that it even had a scent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that he'll take a step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So music can make your\Nblood boil this hard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here he is!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's Arima-kun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.17,0:10:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arima...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.14,0:10:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arima...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.68,0:10:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now even I'm nervous!\NI wanna go to the bathroom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:10:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.85,0:11:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here he is at last, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you ready for your journey?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.25,0:11:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, we're gonna play dodgeball!\NYou can just dodge all the time, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki... I'm in the middle\Nof a lesson with my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat? Not again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.64,0:11:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you get that welt?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was in a hurry, and I bumped my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a klutz, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei, hurry back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.31,0:11:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, that scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.69,0:11:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, my mom's calling me,\NTsubaki. Ask me another time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Okay, then, good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:02.05,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chelsea
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sit yourself down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's begin, Kousei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No running in the halls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.48,0:12:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you your laundry, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.36,0:12:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kousei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did it go? The\NNagai Memorial Competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.95,0:12:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I got first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.53,0:12:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the certificate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.49,0:12:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But Haydn's given you such trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.87,0:12:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I practiced a ton!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your achievements are the\Nbest medicine for me, Kousei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll take first place again!\NIf it makes you better, Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take first place as\Nmany times as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.03,0:13:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's standing still?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't waver. Don't be afraid.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.18,0:13:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit, it's overpowering me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're all afraid, you know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.54,0:14:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's Kousei, under the spotlight again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.71,0:14:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The invincible one, the pianist\Nwho's a breed apart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The one I looked up to...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.92,0:14:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kousei Arima.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's back... His unmatched accuracy. His\Nplaying - like a mirror image of the score.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The stainless steel-like piano\Ninaccessible to the rest of us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.27,0:14:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the Kousei Arima of two years ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can hear the notes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.90,0:14:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My fingers are moving. I can play\Nthe score exactly as I've memorized it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can play on the strength\Nof my muscle memory.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How does the real you want to play this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.08,0:14:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is no different than\Nhow I've always played.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's how it should be.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A musician should be a\Nmirror that reflects the score.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you can't win\Nunless you do it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.01,0:15:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to get first place for\Nme again, aren't you, Kousei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.22,0:15:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were playing the\Npiano this morning again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.31,0:15:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I came to buy food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since my dad's away on business,\N it's for me and my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.61,0:15:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's just egg sandwiches!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.03,0:15:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not very healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she won't let me use a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring you something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.66,0:15:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have oden leftover from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How's your mom doing, Kousei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My mom said she\Nhasn't been feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's going to be hospitalized soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.18,0:15:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.01,0:15:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.76,0:15:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My mom got mad because I couldn't play the\Nway she told me to, and she ruined her health.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I'm gonna take first place,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and make her well again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.74,0:16:02.49,Clang,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First Place - Arima Kousei
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:05.24,Twitch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei Arima - The Child Prodigy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arima's in first again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.49,0:16:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Human Metronome, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just go overseas already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.58,0:16:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bland and innocuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's so in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.21,0:16:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And he's nothing but\Nhis mother's puppet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shut up, shut up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}None of you know\Nwhat you're talking about.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm the only one who's on Mom's side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, my mom's coming\Nfrom the hospital to see me perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.06,0:16:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So your mom's recovered now? That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it's all thanks to that\Nvisit from handsome me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.32,0:16:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And my candy erasers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.03,0:16:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't think Kousei's\Nmom knew what to do with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.66,0:16:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The entrance on the left\Nside, facing the audience.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A spot where I can see her.\NThat's my mom's special seat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.21,0:16:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom's here today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.01,0:17:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in order to make Mom well again,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in order to make her happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna play my very best as a gift for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Saki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just what do you call that performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.28,0:17:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How many times have I told\Nyou to review the score?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.07,0:17:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Saki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.53,0:17:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Too harsh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I've never heard Arima-kun play better....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Misplaying both the third and eleventh measures!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get one of the staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.66,0:17:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You make mistakes like that because\Nyou're drowning in your own emotions!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.92,0:17:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're not going to bed\Nuntil you can play that part.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.64,0:17:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why can't you even play an easy\Npiece like that? You're so worthless!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm in the middle of a lesson with my mom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.81,0:17:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whaaat?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.77,0:17:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Messing up the same part!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That kid's covered with bruises.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:18:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why he always wears long sleeves.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who'd be that harsh with a kid?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.78,0:18:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's a monster.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.41,0:18:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you throw that score -\Nyou should be ashamed of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.50,0:18:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All I wanted was for you to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even when I wanted to play with\NTsubaki and Watari, even when you hit me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I put up with it... I put up\Nwith it, and kept practicing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All I wanted was for you to get better...\NAll I wanted was for you to be happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.06,0:18:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you would just die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:19:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was the last time I\Nsaid anything to my mom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.93,0:19:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to compete in the final?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.34,0:19:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.20,0:19:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since I did get through the prelims.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.27,0:19:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's awful. My\Nmother just passed away,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.19,0:19:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and here I am, worrying about\Nthe competition in a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.49,0:19:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How awful is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure I'm okay. Because that's\N how I was built, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.21,0:19:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't remember my\Nmother's face that day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.67,0:19:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's like there's a big black\Nhole peering back at me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,His mother just passed away, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How can he play the\Npiano like nothing happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's not off by even a fraction.\NIt's business as usual with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's a demonic chip off the old block!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The entrance on the left\Nside, facing the audience.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A spot where I can see her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's my mom's special seat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.91,0:20:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is... this is my punishment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right, this is your punishment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.18,0:20:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You understand that, don't you?\NMy darling, darling little Kousei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The notes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sound of the piano... I can't hear it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.41,0:21:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's starting to unravel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.41,0:21:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,About Arima-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rumor has it that he can't\Nhear the notes anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.06,0:21:20.06,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Resonance
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.01,0:22:38.93,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 10\NThe Place I Was at With You
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.07,0:22:55.08,BTSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Watch Again Next Week!
